  create_atoms CPU = 0.000 seconds

region lower block INF INF -${by} 0.0 INF INF units box
region lower block INF INF -51.6298749020371 0.0 INF INF units box
lattice fcc ${a0} orient x 0 3 -1 orient y 0 1 3 orient z 1 0 0
lattice fcc 4.0817 orient x 0 3 -1 orient y 0 1 3 orient z 1 0 0
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 5.1629875 5.1629875 4.0817
create_atoms 2 region lower
Created 162 atoms
  using lattice units in orthogonal box = (0 -51.629875 0) to (12.907469 51.629875 4.0817)
  create_atoms CPU = 0.000 seconds

group upper type 1
160 atoms in group upper
group lower type 2
162 atoms in group lower

# 3) Settings
pair_style eam/alloy
pair_coeff * * Al_zhou.eam.alloy Al Al
